<br>
That puts them after you guys in the rotation; I noticed however that the rotation indicated that you (Tindi) were up for him; if, for some reason there was confusion about who was up when AD killed the statue, let me know, and I will put them in their required spot so as not to skip you guys in the rotation. <br>
<br>
No worries either way, just want to make sure you get him if he's yours. <br>
<br>
Yers,<br>
