<br>
CoN had entered Kael and had been massing up to do Vindi / Statue . AD came in and stated that they had spoken to NB / Tindi about getting the shot....<br>
<br>
We offered them statue and we'd take vindi..(we bit it this time due to a lagged heal..bleh).<br>
<br>
Anyway...AD was under the assumption that if the guild scheduled gives you the green light..its yours regardless of who is there at that time. I tried to explain to Extrafth that if you are not there at the time you ask permission, and another non rotation guild is there and ready...then the guild there gets the shot.<br>
<br>
In the end AD got the kill..and congrats on getting on rotation.<br>
<br>
I just wanted to clarify this though, since there seemed to be some confusion on the matter last eve. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#222222><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/btherathetravelagency.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ghalidsoulsaver>Ghalid Soulsaver</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://personal.bhm.bellsouth.net/bhm/w/i/wilsonua/pstgif.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Legend of Marr</span><br>  Posts: 193<br> <font color=#00FFFF>(3/15/03 4:30 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm11.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=291.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Statue Rot</span><hr size=1> I do believe you are correct Karas.  Since there were two guilds not currently on the rotation then it would be a race or situation to be worked out between those two guilds.  A rotation guild giving a non rotation guild a shot at the rotation is just them saying &quot;We won't come gank him from you...have at it.&quot;<br>
<br>
Best respect for a situation like that I would think would be for the first guild to take their shot at Vindicator (CoN in this case).  If they succeeded they got Statue as well.  If they failed on Vindicator or even Statue, then I would see no real issue for the next guild (if they were currently in zone and ready to go) getting their shot.<br>
<br>
Ghalid Soulsaver<br>
