</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#222222><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/btherathetravelagency.showUserPublicProfile?gid=extrafth>Extrafth</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Altus Domini</span><br>  Posts: 54<br> <font color=#00FFFF>(3/18/03 2:36 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm11.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=291.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Statue Rot</span><hr size=1> Yeah it was an interesting night to say the very least.  We showed up, and CoN were in Left arena, I immediately started talking with Karas.  I understood that just cause a guild gives a shot that we don't have 100% clearance, was just the 2nd day in a row, we had asked permission and &quot;called off the wolves&quot; in a way, (aka TL and NB) who could have easily killed them with half the people it took us to do.  And was really bothering me, we gave no pressure at all, we zoned in to 16 CoN in zone, 30 minutes later we had 28 people and ready to pull vindi, but as per the conversation I didn't pull CoN still had 16 people in zone and no warriors.  But we waiting around for 2-3 hours for them to get setup and pull, offered any help with pulling, kept all their respawns killed to help them out.  They failed on Vindi, and 5 minutes later we pulled.  I felt really bad, but soon as they died, whole guild was like, they died it's our turn to try right?  So we pulled and killed, many things were said in ooc, lot of it not meant, I tried to shut my guild up, and karas his guild.<br>
<br>
From time we pulled vindi to time statue was dead was no more than 1 hour <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Anyways, was a fun night, thought I would share the story of the night, let Karas know I was not confused but rather sadened to see yet another day of calling off the wolves and seeing another guild in the zone ready to take the mobs out that we had asked the bigger guilds to back away from for the day for us to have a shot. <p>Extrafth Saliva<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--> 65 Ikysaurus Monk<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--> <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=110448" target="top">Extrafth's Loots</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--> <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=137290" target="top">Ralkeem's Loots</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
<br>
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/btherathetravelagency.showUserPublicProfile?gid=karas>Karas</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>CoN - GL</span><br>  Posts: 333<br> <font color=#00FFFF>(3/18/03 1:15 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm11.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=291.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Statue Rot</span><hr size=1> I have to beg to differ in that we *both* had the same amount of people for most of the night...I kept checking it to see if you'd have more than us, and if it was evident you'd be able to take em out before us, I was going to let it happen.<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>And was really bothering me, we gave no pressure at all<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
Well...that's in the eye of the beholder...heh..when you are getting multiple tells from the guild asking you &quot;are you doing Vindi soon?&quot; or &quot;I have to call people overseas to log on so we can do this, and its getting expensive&quot;...or &quot;I'm so tired of calling ppl off only to find others here&quot; etc etc....I'd say that's pressure....<br>
<br>
Normally..If I zone in...see vindi up but hear &quot;We're going to be doing him&quot; from a guild that has 16 at least in zone, its safe to assume more would be on the way...so I leave.<br>
<br>
That is what, from my standpoint, upset me at the time. Sure...there are races to mobs...but these days for mobs like statue / vindi...its not like that. Most will either say &quot;shoot me a tell if you cant take him&quot; or the like.<br>
<br>
<br>
Regardless, whats done is done....we'll have a shot again someday soon. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm11.showPrevMessage?topicID=291.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm11.showNextMessage?topicID=291.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm11.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=291.topic&index=6><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/gfx/addReply1.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm11.emailToFriend?topicID=291.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm11.threadControl?topicID=291.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/deleteThreadFire.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm11.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=291.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm11.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=291.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub6.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1">